t races and ethnic groups experience incarceration. The rate for each specific racial and ethnic group is computed by dividing the population of interest within that group by the total state population for that particular group.</div>\n<br/>\n<div id=\"regular-text\">To calculate the RRI, the rate of each outcome of interest for individuals who are Black non-Hispanic and Hispanic any race, is divided by the rate at which the outcome occurs for individuals who are White. A RRI of 1 indicates no disparity. RRIs greater than 1 indicate the outcome occurs more frequently for individuals who are Black or Hispanic, and an RRI less than 1 indicates an outcome occurs less frequently than for individuals who are White.</div>\n<br/>\n</div>\n```\n:::\n:::\n\n\n::: {.panel-tabset}\n\n### Sentence Length\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); justify-items: center;\">\n<div id=\"htmlwidget-05ce5383f1a1830b7f5f\" style=\"width:100%;height:650px;\" class=\"highchart html-widget \"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-05ce5383f1a1830b7f5f\">{\"x\":{\"hc_opts\":{\"chart\":{\"reflow\":true,\"marginTop\":100,\"marginBottom\":80,\"spacingBottom\":80,\"width\":300,\"height\":300},\"title\":{\"text\":\"Black People, Non-Hispanic\"},\"yAxis\":{\"title\":\"\",\"type\":\"linear\",\"categories\":{\"0\":\" \",\"1\":\"1 = White<br>Reference Line\",\"2\":\" \",\"3\":\" \",\"4\":\" \",\"5\":\" \"},\"labels\":{\"rotation\":0,\"step\":1},\"min\":0,\"max\":5,\"plotBands\":[{\"color\":\"rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)\",\"from\":0,\"to\":1}]},\"credits\":{\"enabled\":false},\"exporting\":{\"enabled\":false},\"boost\":{\"enabled\":false},\"plotOptions\":{\"series\":{\"label\":{\"enabled\":false},\"turboThreshold\":0,\"showInLegend\":true,\"stacking\":\"normal\"},\"treemap\":{\"layoutAlgorithm\":\"squarified\"},\"scatter\":{\"marker\":{\"symbol\":\"circle\"}},\"bar\":{\"dataLabels\":{\"enabled\":true,\"f